article_title: Will A Decision For King Bring Health Care Stocks Crashing Down?

article_metadata.description: Health care stocks have exploded since passage of the Affordable Care Act, in part because of a flood of federal money. Would a decision for King pop that bubble?
article_metadata.author: Merrill Matthews
